INTRODUCTION TO THE PROJECT:

The goal of the project is to apply Software Developing and Testing Life Cycle to the Building Information Modelling (BIM) methodology. 
In this case, BIM sector on the scope is survey of existing building. Goal of the survey is to capture point cloud and to model building in 3D based on the point cloud with information about types and parameters of the objects. 

The project knowledge is based on: 
- CTFL Syllabus 2018 v3.1.1 (ISTQB certification)
- ISO 19650 BIM Building Information Modelling

The project has educational character and a form of training. 
